com.isti.traceview.common
Class Station

java.lang.Object
  com.isti.traceview.common.Station
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable
public class Station
extends Object
implements Comparable, Serializable

Defines the station information. Station list is initialized during startup: such information as longitude, latitude, elevation and depth is loaded from a station configuration file. Class implements an interface "Comparable" to define sort order in the station lists.

Parameters:
stationName - the station name.
network - name of network station belongs
stationLongName - the station long name.
stationLatitude - the station latitude.
stationLongitude - the station longitude.
elevation - station elevation according sea level
depth - depth of station placement
channels - the collection of 'IPlotDataProviderInfo' objects, references to channels of this station
